        "sampleRate": 24000
    }
}
</pre>

<h3>7.2.4 Real-Time Considerations</h3>

<pre>
Latency Management:

For AAC Users:
  - Immediate feedback is critical
  - Pre-generate common phrases
  - Use predictive synthesis
  - Buffer for smooth playback

Optimization Strategies:
  1. Cache frequently used phrases
  2. Use streaming synthesis for long text
  3. Pre-warm TTS engine
  4. Local synthesis when possible
  5. Fallback to simpler voice on high latency

Example - Predictive Caching:
const commonPhrases = [
    "Yes", "No", "Help", "Thank you",
    "I need", "Please", "Stop"
];

// Pre-generate on startup
await talk.pregenerate(commonPhrases);

// Instant playback
aac.on('quickPhrase', (phrase) =&gt; {
    talk.playFromCache(phrase);
});
</pre>

