<h2>7.8 Deployment Considerations</h2>

<h3>7.8.1 System Requirements</h3>

<pre>
Minimum Requirements:

For Basic AAC + TTS:
  - CPU: 2 cores
  - RAM: 4GB
  - Storage: 1GB
  - Network: Optional

For Full Ecosystem:
  - CPU: 4 cores
  - RAM: 8GB
  - Storage: 5GB
  - GPU: Recommended for ISP avatar
  - Network: Required for neural TTS

Mobile Devices:
  - iOS 14+ / Android 10+
  - 3GB RAM minimum
  - Local processing or cloud hybrid
</pre>

<h3>7.8.2 Cloud vs Local Processing</h3>

<pre>
Processing Options:

Fully Local:
  + No internet required
  + Lowest latency
  + Full privacy
  - Higher device requirements
  - Larger app size

Cloud Hybrid:
  + Better TTS quality
  + Smaller app footprint
  + Access to updates
  - Requires internet
  - Variable latency

Recommendation:
  - AAC signal processing: Always local
  - TTS: Local with cloud enhancement
  - ISP: Local avatar, cloud translation
  - Braille: Always local
</pre>

